fields.calculatedFormula: IF( dsfs__Envelope_Status__c  = "Voided",  0,  IF(dsfs__Envelope_Status__c  = "Declined",  0,   IF(dsfs__Envelope_Status__c  = "Sent",  dsfs__Sent_Age__c * 24,  dsfs__Hours_to_Complete__c ) ) )

fields.calculatedFormula:
IF( dsfs__Envelope_Status__c  = "Voided", "",  IF(dsfs__Envelope_Status__c  = "Declined",  "",   IF(dsfs__Envelope_Status__c  = "Sent",  "", TEXT( 
ROUND( 
( dsfs__Completed_Date_Time__c  -  dsfs__Sent_Date_Time__c ) - 
MOD(dsfs__Completed_Date_Time__c  - dsfs__Sent_Date_Time__c,1) 
,0) 
) 
&" day(s), "& 
TEXT( 
ROUND( 
MOD(dsfs__Completed_Date_Time__c - dsfs__Sent_Date_Time__c,1)*24 - 
MOD(MOD(dsfs__Completed_Date_Time__c - dsfs__Sent_Date_Time__c,1)*24,1) 
,0) 
) 
&" hour(s), "& 
TEXT( 
ROUND( 
MOD(MOD(dsfs__Completed_Date_Time__c - dsfs__Sent_Date_Time__c,1)*24,1) 
*60 
,0) 
)&" minute(s)") ) )
